    <div begin="00:00.890" end="03:40.700">
      <p begin="00:00.890" end="00:02.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L1"><span begin="00:00.890" end="00:01.160">誰</span><span begin="00:01.160" end="00:01.290">が</span> <span begin="00:01.350" end="00:01.640">見</span><span begin="00:01.640" end="00:01.800">え</span><span begin="00:01.800" end="00:02.010">る</span> <span begin="00:02.050" end="00:02.130">聞</span><span begin="00:02.200" end="00:02.480">こ</span><span begin="00:02.480" end="00:02.640">え</span><span begin="00:02.640" end="00:02.940">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">有谁 能够看见 能够听见</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">有誰 能夠看見 能夠聽見</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Who can see who can hear</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">누군가 보이고, 들려</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Qui peut me voir ou m'entendre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Quién puede ver puede escuchar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wer kann sehen wer kann hören</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Quem pode ver, pode ouvir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Кого видно кого слышно</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chi riesce a vedere a sentire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Dare ga mieru kikoeru</span></p>
      <p begin="00:03.500" end="00:05.760" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L2"><span begin="00:03.500" end="00:03.800">祈</span><span begin="00:03.800" end="00:03.910">っ</span><span begin="00:03.910" end="00:04.050">てい</span><span begin="00:04.050" end="00:04.380">る</span> <span begin="00:04.440" end="00:04.600">知</span><span begin="00:04.600" end="00:05.000">ろう</span><span begin="00:05.050" end="00:05.190">と</span><span begin="00:05.190" end="00:05.270">し</span><span begin="00:05.340" end="00:05.520">た</span><span begin="00:05.520" end="00:05.610">っ</span><span begin="00:05.610" end="00:05.760">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">祈祷着 即使想要去了解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">祈禱著 即使想要去了解</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Praying even if trying to know</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기도하고 있어, 알려고 해봐도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si j'essaie de savoir qui prie</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estoy rezando aunque intente saberlo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Betend auch wenn man versucht es zu wissen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estou orando mesmo tentando saber</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я молюсь даже если пыталась узнать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sto pregando anche se cercassi di sapere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Inotte iru shirou to shitatte</span></p>
      <p begin="00:05.760" end="00:07.350" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L3"><span begin="00:05.760" end="00:06.080">塞</span><span begin="00:06.080" end="00:06.150">い</span><span begin="00:06.190" end="00:06.330">で</span><span begin="00:06.330" end="00:06.580">る</span> <span begin="00:06.620" end="00:06.920">黙</span><span begin="00:06.920" end="00:07.040">っ</span><span begin="00:07.040" end="00:07.220">てい</span><span begin="00:07.220" end="00:07.350">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">却被阻挡 保持着沉默</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">卻被阻擋 保持著沉默</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Shutting away remaining silent</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">가로막혀 있어, 침묵하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me referme et je reste silencieuse</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estoy bloqueada estoy en silencio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Verschlossen schweigend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estou bloqueando estou em silêncio</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Закрываю уши молчу</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sto bloccando tutto sto rimanendo in silenzio</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Fusaideru damatte iru</span></p>
      <p begin="00:07.900" end="00:10.240" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L4"><span begin="00:07.900" end="00:08.470">走</span><span begin="00:08.490" end="00:08.740">り</span><span begin="00:08.770" end="00:08.970">出</span><span begin="00:09.010" end="00:09.240">し</span><span begin="00:09.330" end="00:09.670">た</span><span begin="00:09.670" end="00:09.850">い</span><span begin="00:09.910" end="00:10.030">の</span><span begin="00:10.070" end="00:10.240">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">明明想要奔跑而出</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">明明想要奔跑而出</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even though wanting to start running</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">달려나가고 싶은데</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Alors que je veux m'élancer</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque quiero salir corriendo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Obwohl ich losrennen möchte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Embora eu queira sair correndo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Хотя так хочу сорваться на бег</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se vorrei iniziare a correre</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hashiridashitai no ni</span></p>
      <p begin="00:10.340" end="00:12.210" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L5"><span begin="00:10.340" end="00:10.510">待</span><span begin="00:10.510" end="00:10.610">っ</span><span begin="00:10.610" end="00:10.780">てい</span><span begin="00:10.780" end="00:11.020">る</span> <span begin="00:11.330" end="00:11.640">届</span><span begin="00:11.640" end="00:11.710">い</span><span begin="00:11.770" end="00:11.920">てい</span><span begin="00:11.920" end="00:12.210">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">等待着 已经传达</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">等待著 已經傳達</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Waiting reaching</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">기다리고 있어, 닿고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'attends et cela me parvient</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estoy esperando está llegando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Wartend es kommt an</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estou esperando está alcançando</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я жду это достигает меня</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sto aspettando ti sta raggiungendo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Matte iru todoite iru</span></p>
      <p begin="00:12.500" end="00:17.510" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L6"><span begin="00:12.500" end="00:12.790">笑</span><span begin="00:12.790" end="00:12.920">っ</span><span begin="00:12.920" end="00:13.080">てい</span><span begin="00:13.080" end="00:13.330">る</span> <span begin="00:13.620" end="00:14.100">面</span><span begin="00:14.190" end="00:14.750">影</span><span begin="00:14.780" end="00:15.790">が</span><span begin="00:15.900" end="00:16.040">凪</span><span begin="00:16.070" end="00:16.530">ぐ</span> <span begin="00:17.040" end="00:17.510">今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">微笑着 往昔的面容重归平静 就在此刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">微笑著 往昔的面容重歸平靜 就在此刻</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Smiling the vestige calms down now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">웃고 있어, 그 옛모습이 잔잔해지는 지금</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je souris et mes vestiges s'apaisent maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estoy sonriendo tu imagen se calma ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Lächelnd die Spuren der Erinnerung beruhigen sich nun</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Estou sorrindo os vestígios se acalmam agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Смеюсь сейчас когда образ успокаивается</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Sto sorridendo le tracce del passato si calmano ora</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Waratte iru omokage ga nagu ima</span></p>
      <p begin="00:37.030" end="00:39.630" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L7"><span begin="00:37.030" end="00:37.270">現</span><span begin="00:37.300" end="00:37.560">実</span><span begin="00:37.630" end="00:37.740">と</span><span begin="00:37.740" end="00:37.820">非</span><span begin="00:37.910" end="00:38.220">対</span><span begin="00:38.310" end="00:38.690">称</span><span begin="00:38.740" end="00:39.630">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">与现实形成非对称</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">與現實形成非對稱</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Asymmetrically with reality</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">현실과 비대칭으로</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">En asymétrie avec la réalité</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Asimétricamente a la realidad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Asymmetrisch zur Realität</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Assimetricamente à realidade</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Асимметрично реальности</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Asimmetrico rispetto alla realtà</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Genjitsu to hitaishou ni</span></p>
      <p begin="00:40.050" end="00:43.340" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L8"><span begin="00:40.050" end="00:40.110">飛</span><span begin="00:40.180" end="00:40.440">ぼう</span><span begin="00:40.480" end="00:40.610">と</span><span begin="00:40.610" end="00:40.720">し</span><span begin="00:40.760" end="00:40.980">た</span><span begin="00:41.020" end="00:41.530">二</span><span begin="00:41.590" end="00:41.830">つ</span><span begin="00:41.910" end="00:42.040">め</span><span begin="00:42.070" end="00:42.210">の</span><span begin="00:42.310" end="00:43.340">身体</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">试图起飞的 第二具身躯</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">試圖起飛的 第二具身軀</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The second body that tried to fly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">날아오르려 했던 두 번째 몸</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce deuxième corps qui tentait de s'envoler</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Un segundo cuerpo que intentó volar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der zweite Körper der zu fliegen versuchte</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O segundo corpo que tentou voar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Второе тело что пыталось взлететь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il secondo corpo che ha cercato di volare</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Tobou to shita futatsume no karada</span></p>
      <p begin="00:43.880" end="00:45.870" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L9"><span begin="00:43.880" end="00:44.130">暗</span><span begin="00:44.130" end="00:44.430">闇</span><span begin="00:44.470" end="00:44.560">で</span><span begin="00:44.610" end="00:44.960">踠</span><span begin="00:44.960" end="00:45.060">い</span><span begin="00:45.190" end="00:45.480">て</span><span begin="00:45.480" end="00:45.630">い</span><span begin="00:45.630" end="00:45.870">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在黑暗中痛苦挣扎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在黑暗中痛苦掙扎</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Struggling in the darkness</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">어둠 속에서 발버둥 치고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Se débat au milieu des ténèbres</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Estoy luchando en la oscuridad</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Sich windend in der Dunkelheit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Está se debatendo na escuridão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Бьётся во тьме</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Si dimena nell'oscurità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kurayami de mogaite iru</span></p>
      <p begin="00:46.170" end="00:48.740" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L10"><span begin="00:46.170" end="00:46.440">真</span><span begin="00:46.460" end="00:46.750">実</span><span begin="00:46.750" end="00:47.000">は</span><span begin="00:47.050" end="00:47.420">平</span><span begin="00:47.500" end="00:47.860">等</span><span begin="00:47.900" end="00:48.740">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真相平等地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真相平等地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Truth will equally</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">진실은 평등하게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vérité de manière égale</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La verdad ataca</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Wahrheit greift gleichermaßen an</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A verdade de forma igualitária</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Истина в равной степени</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La verità in modo equo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjitsu wa byoudou ni</span></p>
      <p begin="00:49.150" end="00:53.320" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L11"><span begin="00:49.150" end="00:49.510">襲</span><span begin="00:49.510" end="00:49.580">い</span><span begin="00:49.630" end="00:49.700">か</span><span begin="00:49.770" end="00:49.890">か</span><span begin="00:49.910" end="00:50.140">る</span> <span begin="00:50.200" end="00:50.730">紅</span><span begin="00:50.760" end="00:50.900">の</span><span begin="00:50.900" end="00:51.310">糸</span><span begin="00:51.340" end="00:51.540">を</span><span begin="00:51.610" end="00:52.400">絡</span><span begin="00:52.480" end="00:52.790">ま</span><span begin="00:52.860" end="00:52.980">せ</span><span begin="00:53.050" end="00:53.320">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">席卷而来 将红线缠绕交织</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">席捲而來 將紅線纏繞交織</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Assault entangling the crimson threads</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">덮쳐와, 붉은 실을 얽어매며</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">S'abat sur moi en emmêlant ses fils cramoisis</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Por igual enredando el hilo carmesí</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Den purpurroten Faden verflechtend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ataca emaranhando o fio carmesim</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Набрасывается сплетая красные нити</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ci assale intrecciando il filo cremisi</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Osoikakaru kurenai no ito o karamasete</span></p>
      <p begin="00:53.640" end="00:55.230" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L12"><span begin="00:53.640" end="00:53.920">確</span><span begin="00:53.920" end="00:54.240">率</span><span begin="00:54.290" end="00:54.580">弾</span><span begin="00:54.610" end="00:54.720">き</span><span begin="00:54.760" end="00:55.100">出</span><span begin="00:55.100" end="00:55.230">す</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">推算出最终的概率</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">推算出最終的概率</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Deriving the probability</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">확률을 산출해 내지</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Établissant de froides probabilités</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Calculando las probabilidades</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Wahrscheinlichkeit berechnend</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Calculando as probabilidades</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Высчитывая вероятности</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Calcolando la probabilità</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakuritsu hajikidasu</span></p>
      <p begin="00:55.630" end="00:59.060" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L13"><span begin="00:55.630" end="00:56.190">あ</span><span begin="00:56.190" end="00:57.950">あ</span> <span begin="00:57.950" end="00:58.240">あ</span><span begin="00:58.240" end="00:59.060">あ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 아아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А-а а-а</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa aa</span></p>
      <p begin="00:59.330" end="01:03.490" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L14"><span begin="00:59.330" end="00:59.500">手</span><span begin="00:59.620" end="00:59.930">繰</span><span begin="00:59.930" end="01:00.190">り</span><span begin="01:00.190" end="01:00.350">寄</span><span begin="01:00.450" end="01:01.190">せ</span> <span begin="01:01.590" end="01:01.760">手</span><span begin="01:01.760" end="01:01.870">を</span><span begin="01:01.920" end="01:02.140">伸</span><span begin="01:02.190" end="01:02.290">ば</span><span begin="01:02.320" end="01:02.610">す</span><span begin="01:02.670" end="01:03.490">者</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">循着丝线 伸出双手之人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">循著絲線 伸出雙手之人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The one who reels in and reaches out a hand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끌어당기며 손을 뻗는 자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Celui qui tire le fil et tend la main</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aquel que tira hacia sí y extiende la mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diejenige die es heranzieht und die Hand ausstreckt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquela que puxa o fio e estende a mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Та кто притягивает к себе и протягивает руку</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Colui che tira a sé colui che allunga la mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Taguriyose te o nobasu mono</span></p>
      <p begin="01:04.780" end="01:08.200" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L15"><span begin="01:04.780" end="01:05.330">あ</span><span begin="01:05.330" end="01:07.040">あ</span> <span begin="01:07.040" end="01:07.320">あ</span><span begin="01:07.320" end="01:08.200">あ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 아아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А-а а-а</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa aa</span></p>
      <p begin="01:08.500" end="01:17.560" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L16"><span begin="01:08.500" end="01:09.640">私</span><span begin="01:09.640" end="01:10.300">は</span> <span begin="01:10.740" end="01:10.960">そ</span><span begin="01:11.060" end="01:11.340">こ</span><span begin="01:11.340" end="01:11.460">に</span><span begin="01:11.490" end="01:11.770">立</span><span begin="01:11.770" end="01:11.880">つ</span> <span begin="01:11.880" end="01:12.210">そ</span><span begin="01:12.210" end="01:12.490">の</span><span begin="01:12.610" end="01:13.080">為</span><span begin="01:13.080" end="01:13.370">に</span><span begin="01:13.880" end="01:15.150">戻</span><span begin="01:15.200" end="01:15.270">る</span><span begin="01:15.340" end="01:15.560">か</span><span begin="01:15.560" end="01:17.560">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我将 伫立于那里 只为那般才会归来</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我將 佇立於那裡 只為那般才會歸來</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I will stand there because I will return for that sake</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 그곳에 설 거야, 그러기 위해 돌아갈 테니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me tiendrai là car je reviens juste pour cela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo estaré allí volveré por ese motivo</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich werde dort stehen denn dafür kehre ich zurück</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu estarei lá porque voltarei para isso</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду стоять там и ради этого я вернусь</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io starò in piedi là perché ritornerò per quel motivo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi wa soko ni tatsu sono tame ni modoru kara</span></p>
      <p begin="01:18.170" end="01:18.790" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L17"><span begin="01:18.170" end="01:18.390">今</span><span begin="01:18.480" end="01:18.610">で</span><span begin="01:18.650" end="01:18.790">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même encore maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst jetzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ancora adesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima demo</span></p>
      <p begin="01:18.880" end="01:20.990" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L18"><span begin="01:18.880" end="01:19.460">心</span><span begin="01:19.480" end="01:19.620">の</span><span begin="01:19.620" end="01:19.880">雨</span><span begin="01:19.880" end="01:19.970">は</span><span begin="01:20.040" end="01:20.120">止</span><span begin="01:20.180" end="01:20.360">ま</span><span begin="01:20.360" end="01:20.470">っ</span><span begin="01:20.470" end="01:20.630">て</span><span begin="01:20.630" end="01:20.790">な</span><span begin="01:20.830" end="01:20.870">く</span><span begin="01:20.910" end="01:20.990">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">心底的雨依然未曾停歇</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">心底的雨依然未曾停歇</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The rain in my heart has not stopped</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음의 비는 그치지 않았고</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La pluie dans mon cœur ne s'est pas arrêtée</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La lluvia en mi corazón no se ha detenido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hat der Regen in meinem Herzen nicht aufgehört</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A chuva no meu coração não parou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Дождь в моем сердце всё еще не прекратился</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La pioggia nel mio cuore non è cessata</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no ame wa tomatte nakute</span></p>
      <p begin="01:21.180" end="01:23.900" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L19"><span begin="01:21.180" end="01:21.570">言</span><span begin="01:21.620" end="01:21.740">葉</span><span begin="01:21.760" end="01:21.890">の</span><span begin="01:21.890" end="01:22.000">意</span><span begin="01:22.050" end="01:22.170">味</span><span begin="01:22.170" end="01:22.290">を</span><span begin="01:22.340" end="01:22.780">放</span><span begin="01:22.780" end="01:22.880">り</span><span begin="01:22.920" end="01:23.080">出</span><span begin="01:23.080" end="01:23.170">し</span><span begin="01:23.200" end="01:23.360">た</span><span begin="01:23.360" end="01:23.480">っ</span><span begin="01:23.480" end="01:23.900">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕抛却言语的意义</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕拋卻言語的意義</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I throw away the meaning of words</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말의 의미를 내팽개친다 해도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je rejette le sens des mots</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque abandone el significado de las palabras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn ich die Bedeutung der Worte wegwerfe</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que eu abandone o significado das palavras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если я отбросила смысл слов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se gettassi via il significato delle parole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kotoba no imi o houridashitatte</span></p>
      <p begin="01:24.610" end="01:26.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L20"><span begin="01:24.610" end="01:24.690">逃</span><span begin="01:24.750" end="01:24.890">げ</span><span begin="01:24.890" end="01:25.050">ら</span><span begin="01:25.050" end="01:25.180">れ</span><span begin="01:25.180" end="01:25.260">は</span><span begin="01:25.280" end="01:25.410">し</span><span begin="01:25.470" end="01:25.650">な</span><span begin="01:25.650" end="01:25.700">い</span><span begin="01:25.700" end="01:26.210">命</span><span begin="01:26.210" end="01:26.460">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这无处可逃的命运中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這無處可逃的命運中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">With a life from which I cannot escape</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도망칠 수 없는 목숨이라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec cette vie dont on ne peut s'échapper</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con esta vida de la que no puedo escapar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mit einem Leben dem ich nicht entfliehen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em uma vida da qual não se pode fugir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В этой жизни от которой не сбежать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In questa vita da cui non posso sfuggire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nigerare wa shinai inochi de</span></p>
      <p begin="01:26.720" end="01:27.950" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L21"><span begin="01:26.720" end="01:27.060">そ</span><span begin="01:27.060" end="01:27.300">れ</span><span begin="01:27.350" end="01:27.540">で</span><span begin="01:27.630" end="01:27.790">も</span><span begin="01:27.790" end="01:27.950">いい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那也无妨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那也無妨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even that is fine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래도 괜찮아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n'est pas grave ainsi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así está bien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das ist in Ordnung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim está tudo bem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть будет так</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi va bene lo stesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo ii</span></p>
      <p begin="01:28.000" end="01:30.170" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L22"><span begin="01:28.000" end="01:28.430">定</span><span begin="01:28.470" end="01:28.610">め</span><span begin="01:28.610" end="01:28.760">ら</span><span begin="01:28.760" end="01:28.840">れ</span><span begin="01:28.900" end="01:29.070">た</span><span begin="01:29.070" end="01:29.260">運</span><span begin="01:29.340" end="01:29.620">命</span><span begin="01:29.620" end="01:29.730">に</span><span begin="01:29.780" end="01:29.930">だ</span><span begin="01:29.930" end="01:30.050">っ</span><span begin="01:30.050" end="01:30.170">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">即使面对注定的命运</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">即使面對注定的命運</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even against the predestined fate</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">정해진 운명이라 해도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même face à un destin déjà tracé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso contra el destino predeterminado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst gegen das vorherbestimmte Schicksal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo contra o destino predeterminado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если против предрешенной судьбы</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche di fronte a un destino già segnato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sadamerareta unmei ni datte</span></p>
      <p begin="01:30.350" end="01:33.080" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L23"><span begin="01:30.350" end="01:30.960">抗</span><span begin="01:30.960" end="01:31.010">い</span><span begin="01:31.060" end="01:31.290">惨</span><span begin="01:31.330" end="01:31.430">め</span><span begin="01:31.480" end="01:31.570">に</span><span begin="01:31.590" end="01:31.850">斃</span><span begin="01:31.890" end="01:32.080">さ</span><span begin="01:32.080" end="01:32.240">れ</span><span begin="01:32.340" end="01:32.530">た</span><span begin="01:32.530" end="01:32.630">っ</span><span begin="01:32.630" end="01:33.080">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">奋起反抗落得惨败而亡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">奮起反抗落得慘敗而亡</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I defy it and am miserably defeated</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">저항하다 처참히 쓰러진다 해도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je suis misérablement abattue en luttant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque me resista y sea derrotada miserablemente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn ich mich wehre und kläglich niedergestreckt werde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que eu resista e seja miseravelmente derrotada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду сопротивляться и буду жалко повержена</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se dovessi oppormi ed essere abbattuta miseramente</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aragai mijime ni taosaretatte</span></p>
      <p begin="01:33.590" end="01:35.810" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L24"><span begin="01:33.590" end="01:33.620">「</span><span begin="01:33.620" end="01:33.810">約</span><span begin="01:33.860" end="01:34.460">束</span><span begin="01:34.460" end="01:34.490">」</span><span begin="01:34.490" end="01:34.790">が</span><span begin="01:34.790" end="01:35.040">あ</span><span begin="01:35.080" end="01:35.440">る</span><span begin="01:35.480" end="01:35.640">か</span><span begin="01:35.640" end="01:35.810">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">因为有着「约定」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">因為有著「約定」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because there is a "promise"</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「약속」이 있으니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Puisqu'il y a notre « promesse »</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque hay una «promesa»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Weil es ein "Versprechen" gibt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Porque existe uma «promessa»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">У меня есть «обещание»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Poiché c'è una «promessa»</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">"Yakusoku" ga aru kara</span></p>
      <p begin="01:36.180" end="01:40.160" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L25"><span begin="01:36.180" end="01:36.780">何</span><span begin="01:36.780" end="01:37.030">度</span><span begin="01:37.070" end="01:37.230">で</span><span begin="01:37.340" end="01:38.030">も</span> <span begin="01:38.060" end="01:38.090">「</span><span begin="01:38.090" end="01:38.130">こ</span><span begin="01:38.190" end="01:38.350">こ</span><span begin="01:38.350" end="01:38.380">」</span><span begin="01:38.380" end="01:38.710">に</span><span begin="01:38.760" end="01:39.350">帰</span><span begin="01:39.350" end="01:39.520">る</span><span begin="01:39.600" end="01:39.920">為</span><span begin="01:39.950" end="01:40.160">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次 为了能够回到「这里」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次 為了能夠回到「這裡」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In order to return "here" again and again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이든 「이곳」으로 돌아가기 위해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour retourner « ici » maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para regresar a «aquí» una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Um immer wieder "hierher" zurückzukehren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para retornar «aqui» não importa quantas vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы раз за разом возвращаться «сюда»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per poter tornare «qui» innumerevoli volte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando demo "koko" ni kaeru tame ni</span></p>
      <p begin="01:40.440" end="01:46.500" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L26"><span begin="01:40.440" end="01:40.560">そ</span><span begin="01:40.600" end="01:41.010">の</span><span begin="01:41.060" end="01:41.300">名</span><span begin="01:41.330" end="01:41.650">を</span><span begin="01:41.650" end="01:41.850">呼</span><span begin="01:41.920" end="01:43.400">ぶ</span><span begin="01:43.890" end="01:44.100">か</span><span begin="01:44.100" end="01:46.500">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我都会呼唤那个名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我都會呼喚那個名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because I will call that name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 이름을 부를 테니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'appellerai ce nom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque gritaré ese nombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Werde ich diesen Namen rufen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu chamarei esse nome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду звать это имя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chiamerò quel nome</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono na o yobu kara</span></p>
      <p begin="02:03.880" end="02:06.440" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L27"><span begin="02:03.880" end="02:04.140">現</span><span begin="02:04.200" end="02:04.460">実</span><span begin="02:04.460" end="02:04.600">は</span><span begin="02:04.630" end="02:04.690">無</span><span begin="02:04.740" end="02:05.090">表</span><span begin="02:05.160" end="02:05.540">情</span><span begin="02:05.630" end="02:06.440">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">现实面无表情地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">現實面無表情地</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Reality expressionlessly</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">현실은 무표정하게</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La réalité sans aucune expression</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La realidad sin expresión</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Realität ist ausdruckslos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A realidade de forma inexpressiva</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Реальность безэмоционально</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La realtà in modo inespressivo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Genjitsu wa muhyoujou ni</span></p>
      <p begin="02:06.890" end="02:11.020" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L28"><span begin="02:06.890" end="02:06.980">噛</span><span begin="02:07.050" end="02:07.190">み</span><span begin="02:07.220" end="02:07.310">付</span><span begin="02:07.340" end="02:07.410">く</span><span begin="02:07.460" end="02:07.910">事</span> <span begin="02:07.910" end="02:08.320">恐</span><span begin="02:08.320" end="02:08.410">れ</span><span begin="02:08.470" end="02:08.560">た</span><span begin="02:08.610" end="02:09.080">牙</span><span begin="02:09.080" end="02:09.240">を</span><span begin="02:09.340" end="02:10.590">携</span><span begin="02:10.590" end="02:10.720">え</span><span begin="02:10.760" end="02:11.020">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">携带着恐惧咬噬的獠牙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">攜帶著恐懼咬噬的獠牙</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Bites carrying the fangs it once feared</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">물어뜯는 것을 두려워한 송곳니를 품고서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Reste immobile arborant ses crocs qui craignent de mordre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Llevando colmillos que temen morder</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mit Reißzähnen die sich davor fürchten zuzubeißen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Carregando presas que temiam morder</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Обнажает клыки что боялись укусить</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mostra le sue zanne timorose di mordere</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kamitsuku koto osoreta kiba o tazusaete</span></p>
      <p begin="02:11.340" end="02:12.680" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L29"><span begin="02:11.340" end="02:11.500">と</span><span begin="02:11.630" end="02:11.970">ど</span><span begin="02:12.060" end="02:12.240">ま</span><span begin="02:12.240" end="02:12.350">っ</span><span begin="02:12.350" end="02:12.510">てい</span><span begin="02:12.510" end="02:12.680">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">停滞不前</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">停滯不前</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Remaining still</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">머물러 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Elle me retient</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Se queda estancada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Bleibt sie stehen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Permanece parada</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">И замирает</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">E rimane ferma</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Todomatte iru</span></p>
      <p begin="02:13.020" end="02:15.730" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L30"><span begin="02:13.020" end="02:13.300">真</span><span begin="02:13.330" end="02:13.590">実</span><span begin="02:13.590" end="02:13.830">は</span><span begin="02:13.900" end="02:14.300">混</span><span begin="02:14.350" end="02:14.720">沌</span><span begin="02:14.770" end="02:15.730">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">真相在混沌之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">真相在混沌之中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Truth aims at the crack</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">진실은 혼돈 속에</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La vérité vise la fissure de la voûte céleste</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La verdad apunta</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Die Wahrheit zielt auf den Riss im blauen Himmel</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A verdade no caos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Истина стремится</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La verità punta</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Shinjitsu wa konton ni</span></p>
      <p begin="02:16.050" end="02:20.170" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L31"><span begin="02:16.050" end="02:16.310">歪</span><span begin="02:16.340" end="02:16.490">め</span><span begin="02:16.490" end="02:16.590">ら</span><span begin="02:16.590" end="02:16.690">れ</span><span begin="02:16.760" end="02:16.990">た</span><span begin="02:17.030" end="02:17.250">蒼</span><span begin="02:17.330" end="02:17.620">穹</span><span begin="02:17.650" end="02:17.720">の</span><span begin="02:17.760" end="02:17.870">亀</span><span begin="02:17.930" end="02:18.360">裂</span> <span begin="02:18.470" end="02:18.840">目</span><span begin="02:18.880" end="02:19.240">指</span><span begin="02:19.300" end="02:19.700">し</span><span begin="02:19.760" end="02:19.880">てい</span><span begin="02:19.880" end="02:20.170">る</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">向着被扭曲的苍穹裂缝 进发</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">向著被扭曲的蒼穹裂縫 進發</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In the azure sky distorted by chaos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">일그러진 푸른 하늘의 균열을 향하고 있어</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Déformée par le chaos le plus total</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Hacia la grieta del cielo azul distorsionado por el caos</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Der durch das Chaos verzerrt wurde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Almeja a fenda no firmamento que foi distorcido</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">К трещине в искаженном хаосом синем небе</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Alla crepa del cielo distorto dal caos</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Yugamerareta soukyuu no kiretsu mezashite iru</span></p>
      <p begin="02:20.470" end="02:22.100" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L32"><span begin="02:20.470" end="02:20.710">確</span><span begin="02:20.750" end="02:21.100">実</span><span begin="02:21.140" end="02:21.460">性</span><span begin="02:21.460" end="02:21.550">に</span><span begin="02:21.600" end="02:21.970">欠</span><span begin="02:22.040" end="02:22.100">く</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">缺乏着确切的定数</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">缺乏著確切的定數</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Lacking certainty</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">확실성이 결여된 채</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Manquant cruellement de certitude</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Carece de certeza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Es mangelt an Gewissheit</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Faltando com a certeza</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Лишенная определенности</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mancando di certezza</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kakujitsusei ni kaku</span></p>
      <p begin="02:22.460" end="02:25.740" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L33"><span begin="02:22.460" end="02:23.040">あ</span><span begin="02:23.040" end="02:24.800">あ</span> <span begin="02:24.800" end="02:25.060">あ</span><span begin="02:25.060" end="02:25.740">あ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 아아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А-а а-а</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa aa</span></p>
      <p begin="02:26.200" end="02:29.940" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L34"><span begin="02:26.200" end="02:26.450">手</span><span begin="02:26.500" end="02:26.800">繰</span><span begin="02:26.800" end="02:27.070">り</span><span begin="02:27.070" end="02:27.200">寄</span><span begin="02:27.330" end="02:27.900">せ</span> <span begin="02:28.500" end="02:28.620">手</span><span begin="02:28.620" end="02:28.750">を</span><span begin="02:28.790" end="02:29.050">伸</span><span begin="02:29.050" end="02:29.130">ば</span><span begin="02:29.170" end="02:29.470">す</span><span begin="02:29.510" end="02:29.940">者</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">循着丝线 伸出双手之人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">循著絲線 伸出雙手之人</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The one who reels in and reaches out a hand</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">끌어당기며 손을 뻗는 자</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Celui qui tire le fil et tend la main</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aquel que tira hacia sí y extiende la mano</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Diejenige die es heranzieht und die Hand ausstreckt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Aquela que puxa o fio e estende a mão</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Та кто притягивает к себе и протягивает руку</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Colui che tira a sé colui che allunga la mano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Taguriyose te o nobasu mono</span></p>
      <p begin="02:31.650" end="02:34.880" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L35"><span begin="02:31.650" end="02:32.210">あ</span><span begin="02:32.210" end="02:33.980">あ</span> <span begin="02:33.980" end="02:34.230">あ</span><span begin="02:34.230" end="02:34.880">あ</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">啊 啊</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">아아 아아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">А-а а-а</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ah ah</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Aa aa</span></p>
      <p begin="02:35.360" end="02:44.670" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L36"><span begin="02:35.360" end="02:36.490">私</span><span begin="02:36.490" end="02:37.100">は</span><span begin="02:37.640" end="02:37.860">そ</span><span begin="02:37.930" end="02:38.230">こ</span><span begin="02:38.230" end="02:38.380">に</span><span begin="02:38.380" end="02:38.610">立</span><span begin="02:38.670" end="02:38.750">つ</span> <span begin="02:38.750" end="02:39.000">そ</span><span begin="02:39.070" end="02:39.370">の</span><span begin="02:39.490" end="02:39.910">為</span><span begin="02:39.930" end="02:40.130">に</span> <span begin="02:40.820" end="02:41.460">も</span><span begin="02:41.460" end="02:42.140">う</span><span begin="02:42.140" end="02:42.490">一</span><span begin="02:42.540" end="02:44.670">度</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我将伫立于那里 只为那般 再来一次</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我將佇立於那裡 只為那般 再來一次</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">I will stand there once again for that sake</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">나는 그곳에 설 거야, 그러기 위해 다시 한번</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Je me tiendrai là une fois de plus pour cela</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Yo estaré allí por ese motivo una vez más</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Ich werde dort stehen dafür noch ein weiteres Mal</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu estarei lá para isso mais uma vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду стоять там и ради этого еще раз</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Io starò in piedi là ancora una volta per quel motivo</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Watashi wa soko ni tatsu sono tame ni mou ichido</span></p>
      <p begin="03:03.320" end="03:03.920" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L37"><span begin="03:03.320" end="03:03.540">今</span><span begin="03:03.610" end="03:03.740">で</span><span begin="03:03.800" end="03:03.920">も</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">事到如今</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even now</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">지금도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même encore maintenant</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Incluso ahora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Selbst jetzt</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo agora</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже сейчас</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Ancora adesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Ima demo</span></p>
      <p begin="03:04.040" end="03:06.130" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L38"><span begin="03:04.040" end="03:04.590">心</span><span begin="03:04.620" end="03:04.710">の</span><span begin="03:04.750" end="03:04.840">場</span><span begin="03:04.890" end="03:05.050">所</span><span begin="03:05.050" end="03:05.140">は</span><span begin="03:05.210" end="03:05.310">変</span><span begin="03:05.340" end="03:05.520">わ</span><span begin="03:05.520" end="03:05.620">っ</span><span begin="03:05.620" end="03:05.740">て</span><span begin="03:05.770" end="03:05.920">な</span><span begin="03:05.970" end="03:06.020">く</span><span begin="03:06.040" end="03:06.130">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">心的居所依然未曾改变</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">心的居所依然未曾改變</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The place of my heart has not changed</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">마음이 있는 곳은 변하지 않아서</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La place de mon cœur n'a pas changé</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">El lugar de mi corazón no ha cambiado</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Hat sich der Ort meines Herzens nicht verändert</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">O lugar do meu coração não mudou</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Место моего сердца осталось прежним</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Il luogo del mio cuore no non è cambiato</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kokoro no basho wa kawatte nakute</span></p>
      <p begin="03:06.330" end="03:09.200" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L39"><span begin="03:06.330" end="03:06.700">言</span><span begin="03:06.760" end="03:06.850">葉</span><span begin="03:06.890" end="03:07.020">の</span><span begin="03:07.020" end="03:07.400">刃</span><span begin="03:07.440" end="03:07.520">が</span><span begin="03:07.590" end="03:07.920">飛</span><span begin="03:07.920" end="03:07.990">び</span><span begin="03:08.080" end="03:08.240">交</span><span begin="03:08.240" end="03:08.370">っ</span><span begin="03:08.370" end="03:08.540">た</span><span begin="03:08.540" end="03:08.670">っ</span><span begin="03:08.670" end="03:09.200">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕言语的利刃交错飞舞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕言語的利刃交錯飛舞</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if blades of words fly around</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">말의 칼날이 난무한다 해도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si les lames des mots volent de toutes parts</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque vuelen espadas de palabras</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn Klingen aus Worten umherfliegen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que lâminas de palavras voem ao redor</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если вокруг летают клинки слов</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se volassero lame di parole</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kotoba no yaiba ga tobikattatte</span></p>
      <p begin="03:09.790" end="03:11.610" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L40"><span begin="03:09.790" end="03:09.850">逃</span><span begin="03:09.930" end="03:10.060">げ</span><span begin="03:10.060" end="03:10.200">ら</span><span begin="03:10.200" end="03:10.320">れ</span><span begin="03:10.320" end="03:10.400">は</span><span begin="03:10.460" end="03:10.570">し</span><span begin="03:10.620" end="03:10.770">な</span><span begin="03:10.770" end="03:10.810">い</span><span begin="03:10.810" end="03:11.270">命</span><span begin="03:11.310" end="03:11.610">で</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">在这无处可逃的命运中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">在這無處可逃的命運中</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">With a life from which I cannot escape</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">도망칠 수 없는 목숨이라</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Avec cette vie dont on ne peut s'échapper</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Con esta vida de la que no puedo escapar</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Mit einem Leben dem ich nicht entfliehen kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Em uma vida da qual não se pode fugir</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">В этой жизни от которой не сбежать</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">In questa vita da cui non posso sfuggire</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nigerare wa shinai inochi de</span></p>
      <p begin="03:11.880" end="03:13.080" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L41"><span begin="03:11.880" end="03:12.200">そ</span><span begin="03:12.200" end="03:12.460">れ</span><span begin="03:12.490" end="03:12.650">で</span><span begin="03:12.760" end="03:12.950">も</span><span begin="03:12.950" end="03:13.080">いい</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">那也无妨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">那也無妨</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even that is fine</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그래도 괜찮아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Ce n'est pas grave ainsi</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aun así está bien</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das ist in Ordnung</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo assim está tudo bem</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Пусть будет так</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Mi va bene lo stesso</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Soredemo ii</span></p>
      <p begin="03:13.150" end="03:15.300" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L42"><span begin="03:13.150" end="03:13.710">儚</span><span begin="03:13.760" end="03:13.830">く</span><span begin="03:13.900" end="03:14.030">消</span><span begin="03:14.030" end="03:14.120">え</span><span begin="03:14.200" end="03:14.250">て</span><span begin="03:14.300" end="03:14.430">し</span><span begin="03:14.490" end="03:14.670">ま</span><span begin="03:14.670" end="03:14.840">うん</span><span begin="03:14.920" end="03:15.100">だ</span><span begin="03:15.100" end="03:15.210">っ</span><span begin="03:15.210" end="03:15.300">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕会如幻影般消散</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕會如幻影般消散</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if I disappear ephemerally</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">덧없이 사라져버린다 해도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si je dois disparaître de façon éphémère</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque desaparezca efímeramente</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn ich flüchtig verschwinde</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que eu desapareça de forma efêmera</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если я эфемерно исчезну</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se dovessi svanire in modo effimero</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Hakanaku kiete shimaun datte</span></p>
      <p begin="03:15.480" end="03:18.140" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L43"><span begin="03:15.480" end="03:15.740">彼</span><span begin="03:15.740" end="03:16.020">方</span><span begin="03:16.040" end="03:16.180">に</span><span begin="03:16.180" end="03:16.330">意</span><span begin="03:16.330" end="03:16.600">識</span><span begin="03:16.600" end="03:16.730">を</span><span begin="03:16.780" end="03:17.080">追</span><span begin="03:17.080" end="03:17.160">い</span><span begin="03:17.160" end="03:17.370">や</span><span begin="03:17.370" end="03:17.470">っ</span><span begin="03:17.470" end="03:17.660">た</span><span begin="03:17.660" end="03:17.760">っ</span><span begin="03:17.760" end="03:18.140">て</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">哪怕将意识驱逐至远方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">哪怕將意識驅逐至遠方</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Even if my consciousness is driven to the far distance</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">저편으로 의식을 몰아낸다 해도</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Même si ma conscience est chassée vers le lointain</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Aunque destierre mi conciencia a la distancia</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Auch wenn mein Bewusstsein in die Ferne getrieben wird</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Mesmo que eu afaste a minha consciência para o além</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Даже если мое сознание будет отброшено вдаль</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Anche se la coscienza venisse scacciata lontano</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Kanata ni ishiki o oiyattatte</span></p>
      <p begin="03:18.720" end="03:21.050" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L44"><span begin="03:18.720" end="03:18.750">「</span><span begin="03:18.750" end="03:18.960">約</span><span begin="03:19.020" end="03:19.600">束</span><span begin="03:19.600" end="03:19.630">」</span><span begin="03:19.630" end="03:19.820">は</span><span begin="03:19.890" end="03:20.240">消</span><span begin="03:20.240" end="03:20.650">え</span><span begin="03:20.650" end="03:20.810">な</span><span begin="03:20.810" end="03:21.050">い</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">「约定」绝对不会消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">「約定」絕對不會消失</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">The "promise" will not vanish</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">「약속」은 사라지지 않아</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">La « promesse » ne s'effacera jamais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">La «promesa» no desaparecerá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Das "Versprechen" wird nicht verschwinden</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">A «promessa» não desaparecerá</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">«Обещание» не исчезнет</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">La «promessa» non svanirà</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">"Yakusoku" wa kienai</span></p>
      <p begin="03:21.330" end="03:25.260" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L45"><span begin="03:21.330" end="03:21.910">何</span><span begin="03:21.910" end="03:22.190">度</span><span begin="03:22.190" end="03:22.380">で</span><span begin="03:22.470" end="03:23.150">も</span><span begin="03:23.170" end="03:23.200">「</span><span begin="03:23.200" end="03:23.270">こ</span><span begin="03:23.310" end="03:23.470">こ</span><span begin="03:23.470" end="03:23.500">」</span><span begin="03:23.500" end="03:23.890">に</span><span begin="03:23.920" end="03:24.500">戻</span><span begin="03:24.500" end="03:24.700">る</span><span begin="03:24.770" end="03:25.070">為</span><span begin="03:25.070" end="03:25.260">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次 为了能够回到「这里」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次 為了能夠回到「這裡」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">In order to return "here" again and again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이든 「이곳」으로 돌아가기 위해</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour revenir « ici » maintes et maintes fois</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para volver a «aquí» una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Um immer wieder "hierher" zurückzukehren</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para voltar «aqui» não importa quantas vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы раз за разом возвращаться «сюда»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per poter tornare «qui» innumerevoli volte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando demo "koko" ni modoru tame ni</span></p>
      <p begin="03:25.600" end="03:29.720" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L46"><span begin="03:25.600" end="03:25.700">そ</span><span begin="03:25.740" end="03:26.150">の</span><span begin="03:26.190" end="03:26.480">名</span><span begin="03:26.480" end="03:26.760">を</span><span begin="03:26.760" end="03:27.000">呼</span><span begin="03:27.040" end="03:28.820">ぶ</span><span begin="03:28.990" end="03:29.190">か</span><span begin="03:29.190" end="03:29.720">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我都会呼唤那个名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我都會呼喚那個名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because I will call that name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 이름을 부를 테니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'appellerai ce nom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque gritaré ese nombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Werde ich diesen Namen rufen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu chamarei esse nome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду звать это имя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chiamerò quel nome</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono na o yobu kara</span></p>
      <p begin="03:30.470" end="03:34.460" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L47"><span begin="03:30.470" end="03:31.050">何</span><span begin="03:31.050" end="03:31.350">度</span><span begin="03:31.350" end="03:31.530">で</span><span begin="03:31.620" end="03:31.940">も</span><span begin="03:32.290" end="03:32.320">「</span><span begin="03:32.320" end="03:32.380">こ</span><span begin="03:32.450" end="03:32.600">こ</span><span begin="03:32.600" end="03:32.630">」</span><span begin="03:32.630" end="03:33.070">で</span><span begin="03:33.070" end="03:33.340">在</span><span begin="03:33.340" end="03:33.500">り</span><span begin="03:33.590" end="03:34.030">続</span><span begin="03:34.060" end="03:34.190">く</span><span begin="03:34.190" end="03:34.340">よう</span><span begin="03:34.340" end="03:34.460">に</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">无论多少次 为了能继续存在于「这里」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">無論多少次 為了能繼續存在於「這裡」</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">So that I can continue to exist "here" again and again</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">몇 번이든 「이곳」에 계속 존재할 수 있도록</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">Pour continuer d'exister « ici » à jamais</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Para seguir existiendo «aquí» una y otra vez</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Damit ich immer wieder "hier" weiter existieren kann</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Para continuar a existir «aqui» não importa quantas vezes</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Чтобы раз за разом продолжать существовать «здесь»</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Per poter continuare a esistere «qui» innumerevoli volte</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Nando demo "koko" de aritsuzuku you ni</span></p>
      <p begin="03:34.720" end="03:40.700" ttm:agent="v1" itunes:key="L48"><span begin="03:34.720" end="03:34.830">そ</span><span begin="03:34.900" end="03:35.320">の</span><span begin="03:35.340" end="03:35.610">名</span><span begin="03:35.610" end="03:35.940">を</span><span begin="03:35.940" end="03:36.160">呼</span><span begin="03:36.200" end="03:37.640">ぶ</span><span begin="03:38.140" end="03:38.380">か</span><span begin="03:38.380" end="03:40.700">ら</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">我都会呼唤那个名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hant">我都會呼喚那個名字</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="en">Because I will call that name</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ko">그 이름을 부를 테니까</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="fr">J'appellerai ce nom</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="es">Porque gritaré ese nombre</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="de">Werde ich diesen Namen rufen</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="pt">Eu chamarei esse nome</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="ru">Я буду звать это имя</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="it">Chiamerò quel nome</span><span ttm:role="x-roman">Sono na o yobu kara</span></p>
    </div>
  </body>
</tt>
